            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1276424</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>SteelSeries 近日推出了一款專為 PlayStation 設計的無線耳機「Arctis GameBuds」，這款真無線耳機同時支援藍牙 5.3 與 2.4GHz 高速無線轉接器，在遊戲機使用時可享受超低延遲的音響；而切換到藍牙模式後，又可直接連接智能手機、電腦，可説是相當方便。以下小編就會做更詳細評測，看看耳機整體表現。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03909.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276426" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03909-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03909-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03909.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03906.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276425" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03906-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03906-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03906.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>2.4GHz 轉接器同藍牙兩用</h2><p>就如剛才提及，SteelSeries Arctis GameBuds 支援 2.4GHz 高速無線轉接器。在充電盒內，你可找到一個 USB-C 介面的手指。只要將它插上 PlayStation 遊戲機的 USB-C 接口，就可在耳機上聽到遊戲機的音響。耳機咪高鋒亦可作遊戲、聊天室內的通話用途。轉接器模式、藍牙模式切換很方便，預設設定中，用家只要按 3 下右邊耳機上的按鈕便可。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03910.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276427" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03910-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03910-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03910.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03898.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276429" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03898-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03898-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03898.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03899.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276431" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03899-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03899-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03899.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲連接遊戲機的 2.4GHz 無線轉接器，基本解決玩遊戲時的聲音延遲問題</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03902.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276430" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03902-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03902-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03902.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲安裝於 PS5 的 USB-C 插口便可</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03916.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276434" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03916-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03916-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03916.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲你可在手機 App 中找到不同 PlayStation 遊戲專用設定，在不同遊戲中享有特別的專用聲效調校。配合 3D 效果，在遊戲中可以好清晰感應到敵人的定位；</p><p>這個 USB-C 無線音響轉接器除了能用於 PlayStation 遊戲機外，也能應用於 Nintendo Switch 遊戲機、電腦（包括 Windows/Mac 電腦）、iPhone 或 Android 智能電話、VR 裝置，但就不適用於 Xbox 遊戲機。只要將轉接器插上電腦、電話、遊戲機上的 USB-C 插口，在裝置上選取使用 Arctis GameBuds 輸出音訊即可使用。而除了 USB-C 之外，耳機隨附一個 USB-C 至 USB-A 轉接器，方便連接較舊電腦。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03913.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276432" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03913-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03913-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03913.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03912.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276433" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03912-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03912-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03912.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在 Nintendo Switch 使用時可辨認為 USB 音響</p><p>當然如果你的電腦、智能電話內置藍牙功能，就可用 Arctis GameBuds 的藍牙模式連接。在耳機上，連續按三下耳機上的按鈕，即可切換轉接器模式／藍牙模式。在晚間享受遊戲，你更可使用 Arctis GameBuds 內置的主動降噪、透明模式。耳機內置有 4 咪高風結合 ANC 技術，過濾外界噪音。而在透明模式讓你在需要時，聽取周圍環境聲音。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03921-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276451" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03921-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03921-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03921-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03908.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276428" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03908-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03908-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03908.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>超過 100 款 PS5 遊戲的音效預設檔</h2><p>配合 iOS／Android 的耳機專用 Arctis Companion 手機程式，你可切換超過 100 種音效設定，包括很多 PS5 遊戲，實時專門為該遊戲調整的音效，以增強沉浸感。我們就嘗試過《The Last of Us II》《Gran Turismo 7》，在緊湊的冒險遊戲、賽車遊戲都很準確定位來自於四面八方的聲音。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03914.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276441" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03914-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03914-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03914.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03917.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276435" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03917-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03917-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03917.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在試玩賽車遊戲也能體驗到很強重低音音效，以及分辨到其他對手的定位</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
